{
  "id": "adv_main_03_12_05",
  "title": "BIG4編1章60話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_thrx-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇと、今日はよろしくお願いします\nでも……今回はどうして引き受けてくれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ thanks in advance for today‚\nBut…why did you agree to this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、なんか勘違いしてません？\n月ストのためとか、別にそういうのじゃないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ aren't you misunderstanding something?\nIt's not for Moon Tempest or anything like that‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6080026413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、仕事と言ってましたね……\n三枝さんが何か条件を出したりしたんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You did say it was work…\n…Did Saegusa-san offer any conditions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "秘密です。わざわざ言う理由なんてありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a secret‚ There’s no reason for me to tell you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6465983707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "う～わ、山田さんてばかっこつけちゃって、ウケる～\n特別手当の金額見て、真っ先にOKしたくせに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh‚ Yamada-san’s trying to act cool‚ how funny\nYou were the first to say OK after seeing the special allowance amount‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5382083097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "山田さん、お金大好きだもんね～\n札束チラつかされたら簡単になびいちゃうよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yamada-san‚ you love money so much~\nYou’re easily swayed by a wad of cash~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4382083097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 47.6020851311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "あんただって、超有名インフルエンサーと\n共演出来るってだけでほいほいOKしてたでしょうが！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were all over it too when you found out you could\nwork with a super famous influencer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にしないでくれますー？　今バズりまくってる人の\n動画チャンネルに三回連続でゲスト出演出来るんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t lump me in with you~‚ I get to guest-star on the video channel\nof someone who’s super popular right now three times in a row‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1248857021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "その子の事務所とプレタポルテの仲が最悪で、今まで\n絡めなかったんだけど、三枝さんが繋いでくれてさぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That person’s agency and Pret-a-Porter have the worst relationship‚ so we couldn’t\nwork together until now‚ but Saegusa-san connected us‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6457365829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "だからあんただって、人参に釣られただけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you were lured by a carrot too‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2061895211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2601576964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "こ、ここ、こういう怖さを\n見たかった訳じゃないですわよ～……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-T-This isn’t the kind of scary\nI was hoping for…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2997047582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、franさん、そのくらいで……\nでも、あれ……mihoさんは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kana-san‚ Fran-san‚ that’s enough…\nBut‚ um…where’s Miho-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 89.130542918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "私はそこの欲まみれの二人と違って\n報酬は求めていません。ただ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unlike those two greedy ones over there‚\nI don’t want any reward‚ However…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……見届けたいものがある。それだけです\nさあ、時間は限られているんだから早く始めましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…there’s something I want to witness‚ That’s all‚\nNow‚ time is limited‚ so let’s get started‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "私達を指名した理由は察しがつくわ。スリクスを\n仮想どりきゅんとでも見立てているんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can guess why you nominated us‚ You’re planning on using IIIX as\npractice dummies for DoriKyun‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "言っておくけど、仲良しこよしで練習する気はないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just to let you know‚ I have no intention of practicing all buddy-buddy with you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.348320679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……私達はサニピやトリエル、リズノワと\n練習する時だって、馴れ合ってるつもりはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We don’t intend to get chummy\nwhen we practice with Sunny Peace‚ TRINITYAiLE‚ or LizNoir either‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～ん、じゃあさ、ダラダラ一緒に練習しても\n意味ないし。いっそライブバトルだけぶっ通しでやる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm~‚ then there’s no point in practicing together if we’re just going to drag it out‚\nWhy don’t we just have a non-stop live battle?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1159629345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "耐久でライブバトル……ですか\n分かりました。ぜひよろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An endurance live battle…?\nUnderstood‚ It would be an honor!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "（I-UNITYでは敵わなかったけど……）\n（私達だって成長した。今なら……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I couldn’t stand up to them at I-UNITY‚ but…）\n（We’ve grown too‚ Now…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_live-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 151.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（こうして合同練習……耐久ライブバトルが始まった）\n（今の月ストなら、スリクスにも引けは取らないはずだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And so the joint practice…the endurance live battle began‚）\n（With Moon Tempest as they are now‚ they should be able to hold their own against IIIX‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 162.3362808269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ。一戦目は私達の勝ちね\n休んでる暇はないわ。すぐに二戦目に移るわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Whew‚ The first round is our win‚\nNo time to rest‚ We’re moving on to the second round immediately‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ま、負けた……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We…lost…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.8712259016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　何ショック受けてんの？　何様だっつーの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah? Why are you so shocked? Who do you think you are?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1234255594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "成長したつもりなのか知らないけど、私達だって\n強くなってるのよ。当然の結果でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You may think you've grown‚ but we've gotten stronger too‚\nThis is a natural outcome‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.477051461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達なら、サニピにだって勝てるわ\nこの程度だなんて、正直期待外れね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With the way we are now‚ we could even beat Sunny Peace‚\nThis is honestly disappointing‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_12_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……もう一回勝負して下さい\n今度は負けません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Please give us another match‚\nWe won’t lose this time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
