      "text": "私達にも収穫はあったわ\n貴方達の手の内は十分に理解したし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We gained something from this too‚\nI’ve fully understood your strategies‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 406.9333353678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
