      "text": "……これだけ付き合わせたからには\nこれ以上、無様なところは見せないでほしいものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…now that we've practiced so much\n…I’d prefer not to see you make a fool of yourselves any more than this‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 412.0000020344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
