      "text": "連戦の中で、スリクスの美学やこだわり、意志の強さを\nより深く感じ取ることが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the midst of our continuous battles‚ I was able to feel IIIX’s aesthetics‚ persistence‚ and strength of will\nmore deeply‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 450.5000020344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
