      "text": "何度も見てるとさ、「あ、ここは絶対に妥協\n出来ないポイントなんだな」ってとこが分かるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After watching them so many times‚\nI can now tell the points where they’re absolutely uncompromising‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 457.1333353678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
